Blur
====

Blur is a NoSQL data store built on top of Lucene, Hadoop, Thrift, 
and Zookeeper.  Tables consist of a series of shards (Lucene indexes)
that are distributed across a cluster of commodity servers.

Mail List
----
blur-user@incubator.apache.org or blur-dev@incubator.apache.org

Documentation
----

Check out the docs/ directory and use the index.html as a starting point.
